overview: AY9ONA, following in the footsteps of an icon of Moroccan rap. From the heights of Ahouli to the Marrakech studio, Laklila set out to meet L'Morphine and Mehdi, two facets of an authentic and timeless artist. In short, a legend who left his mark on the national scene for 16 years. Rappers Small X, Nessyou, Raid, and Hamza 15-3 attest to this.
title: L'Morphine - AY9ONA
